listitem.para:
If the &pos; terminal boots for the first time, its
      &confmac; file does not exist yet. The &pos;
     terminal must first register on the system.

The Graphical image should only be used for &pos; systems with
     storage media such as hard disk or flash medium. Otherwise, the &pos;
     system must be upgraded with enough RAM to hold the system image.
